{"tid":792191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★傳 3 款新 iPhone 轉用支那零件！","createTime":"2018-08-24T11:09:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T13:37:09.000Z","uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0840c049d001a9a9bcfee4f46e031f8c4c05c04a","tid":792191,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://timg.eprice.com.hk/hk/mobile/img/2018-08/23/211265/uniqlo_1_879c9fa1c72243d5208a80fa86055125.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.hk%2Fhk%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2018-08%2F23%2F211265%2Funiqlo_1_879c9fa1c72243d5208a80fa86055125.jpg&h=5de3f4b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據 DigiTimes 的報導，原本為 Apple 提供電池模組的台灣公司新普科技，最近已經改為向電動單車公司供應零件，而稍後發表新 iPhone 和其他 Apple 產品的電池亦會<span style=\"color: red;\">改由大陸公司得賽集團和欣旺達提供</span>。原本為 Apple 供應商的台灣外殼代工生產商可成科技，由於 Apple <span style=\"color: red;\">改用工藝較弱的大陸公司長盈精密技術</span>，結果需要重新尋找客戶。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/211265/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F211265%2F&d=4XEq6ua5ntFi6U7Cv1vYxozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=555fb7f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/211265/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad36f27c9a5bc563b8638240f2067c44b63dae57","tid":792191,"uid":199016,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"63757833196250a39d67f63981c94281f5a2edb2","tid":792191,"uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T11:11:29.000Z","msg":"not a dream<br />\n<br />\n<im